{
  "texts": [
    "This holistic understanding is essential for tasks that require a comprehensive interpretation of the visual scene (Maurício et al. 2022).",
    "The architecture of ViT is mainly based on the original transformer, as shown in Fig. 8.",
    "ViT achieves good results when it is pre-trained on large quantities of data and transferred to various mid-sized or small image recognition platforms (CIFAR-100, ImageNet, VTAB, etc.)",
    "while substantially requiring very few CPU resources to train (Dosovitskiy et al. 2020).",
    "After being proposed by Vaswani et al. (2017) for machine translation, transformers are now the most advanced method for many NLP tasks."
  ]
}